data.description: This beautiful property located on Windsor Downs Drive is sure to impress. The house features spacious rooms, high ceilings, and plenty of natural light. The kitchen boasts modern appliances, granite countertops, and ample cabinet space.  Brand new HVAC! The backyard with new privacy fence is perfect for entertaining, with a large patio area and a well-maintained lawn. This home is located in a peaceful neighborhood and is ideal for families or those seeking a quiet retreat. Don't miss your chance to make this stunning property your new home.
